circumstances.circumstancesOfDisappearance:
On the evening of 11/07/1981, Amber Scholz went to a party in Rock Springs with her boyfriend and another friend. She left the party around 3:00 - 3:30 AM with another friend who escorted her back to her residence at Plaza Court Apartments. That was the last reported sighting of Amber. 

There was no sign of a struggle or forced entry into her home. Her purse and wallet were found in the kitchen, along with a payroll check from her job at a local cleaning service. 

Investigators determined that she was probably preparing her monthly budget when she left her apartment. Amber was engaged in a custody battle over her son with her ex-boyfriend at the time of her disappearance.

circumstances.circumstancesOfDisappearance: On June 17, 2017, Michael Bullinger was last seen (on video) driving through the entrance station of Grand Teton National Park in Moran, Wyoming. After that, Bullinger was never seen again. On June 23, 2017, his car was discovered abandoned in the Pacific Creek Campground, site #4 (approximately 10 miles from the entrance station). After multiple extensive searches, no physical evidence was recovered from his person, nor was his body ever recovered.

Silas Ojeda was last seen on October 23, 2016 in Laramie County, Wyoming. Based upon the investigation, it is likely Silas is deceased. It is believed his body was disposed of in a dumpster in Laramie County prior to the dumpster contents being taken to a landfill in Weld County, Colorado. The landfill was searched but he wasn’t located prior to the search being terminated. At this time there is no credible evidence indicating his remains might be located anywhere else.

circumstances.circumstancesOfDisappearance: Renee Diane Yeargain has been missing from Torrington, Wyoming since August 10, 2004. Two days later, on August 12, 2004, Yeargain's white 1987 Pontiac Subaru station wagon was found at a rest stop between Cheyenne and Torrington, Wyoming. Her keys, cellular phone, and her purse, which contained her wallet, checkbook and other items, were inside the vehicle. No money was found and Yeargain's tattoo kit and clothing were also missing. The car had been parked at the rest area since August 10, 2014.
